high_descs: Take a step to the right, face the sink.
Pick up the coffee cup in the sink.
Turn around, walk to the fridge.
Put the coffee cup by the plate in the fridge for a few seconds, take the coffee cup back out.
Turn around, walk to the coffee pot.
Place the coffee cup on the coffee pot.
anns.task_desc: Place the cold coffee cup on the coffee pot.

high_descs: Turn right, take one step, then stand in front of the sink.
Pick up the white cup in the right side of the sink.
Turn around then walk towards the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door, then place the white cup in the center on the top shelf, then close the door.
Turn left then walk towards the wall, turn left then walk towards the coffee maker.
Place the white cup in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a white cup in the coffee maker.

high_descs: Move to face the sink to the right.
Pick up the mug in the sink.
Turn around, bring the mug to the fridge.
Chill the mug in the fridge.
Turn around with the chilled mug, bring the mug to the coffee machine right of the sink.
Put the chilled mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug on the coffee machine.
